<article class="introduction">
  <header>
    <h1>DICIS Activities</h1>
  </header>
  <p>DICIS will concretize the goals set above by organizing topical open access seminars on particular issues in relation to DH and cinema studies,  initiating regular collaborative publications and facilitating the international mobility of experts.</p><p>The DICIS network wants to keep the organization of the meetings as open, flexible and fluid as possible, leaving the structure of the seminars, the organization, planning, onset and goal open for interpretation by a designated moderator or curator.</p>
</article>

<ul class="activities accordion-tabs">
  <li class="tab-header-and-content">
    <a href="#" class="is-active tab-link">Forthcoming Activities</a>
    <div class="tab-content">
      <% data.current_activities.each do |activity| %>
        <%= partial "activity", locals: { activity: activity } %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </li>
  <li class="tab-header-and-content">
    <a href="#" class="tab-link">Past Activities</a>
    <div class="tab-content">
      <% data.past_activities.each do |activity| %>
        <%= partial "activity", locals: { activity: activity } %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </li>
</ul>

<script>
$(document).ready(function () {
  $('.accordion-tabs').each(function(index) {
    $(this).children('li').first().children('a').addClass('is-active').next().addClass('is-open').show();
  });

  $('.accordion-tabs').on('click', 'li > a', function(event) {
    if (!$(this).hasClass('is-active')) {
      event.preventDefault();
      var accordionTabs = $(this).closest('.accordion-tabs');
      accordionTabs.find('.is-open').removeClass('is-open').hide();

      $(this).next().toggleClass('is-open').toggle();
      accordionTabs.find('.is-active').removeClass('is-active');
      $(this).addClass('is-active');
    } else {
      event.preventDefault();
    }
  });
});
</script>
